≠In Loving Memory of Michael John Eccles
"Ecky"
1965 ~ 2009
Son of Lichfield, so tragically taken
"You'll Never Walk Alone"
Always in our thoughts, forever in our hearts"į
≠Presented to The Sheriff of Lichfield
Dr Daryl Brown
8th May 2021
At the opening of the restored
Gallows Reach section.
of the Heritage Towpath Trail
on the Lichfield Canal."∑
īKathleen Bird 
100 yrs.
So many memories with still more to come
Sit here and enjoy the little things in life
because one day you'll look back and realise
they were the big things."Ő
